instruction: Describe the person who had the biggest impact on your life.
output: The person who had the biggest impact on my life is my grandmother. She has always been there for me and offered her unending support and guidance. She has always encouraged me to pursue my passions and do my best, and not to give up in the face of difficulties. Through her positive attitude and wisdom, she has shown me how to persevere and believe in myself. Most importantly, she has taught me the value of kindness, compassion and love.
